name: electro-fisher
description: /*[---- LOG ENTRY 34 (___) When we deployed our ops the hopes were high to score a new record but that washed away quick. The equipment is close to the brink and so are we. Miscalculations made this our worse season yet and we still have 5 more to go before the session is over. Hopefully we can get our shit together but I don’t think the Lieutenants will allow that. The past few days they have been acting extremely off and we continue to extract this site even though it has already been drained. I’m not sure what their plan is, either way I’m sleeping with one eye open. (]----*\
